---
title: Honey & Thyme Haloumi Couscous Bowl with Roasted Veggies & Lemony Yoghurt
description: There was complete mayhem when this dish hit our tasting table. With sweet honey and fragrant thyme on warm, salty haloumi, plus spiced veggies and toasty flaked almonds, it disappeared from the bowl in record time. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-thyme-haloumi-couscous-bowl-6660c9e9.jpg
